    "txt_content": " 本帖最后由 ab75654 于 2011-3-22 23:27 编辑 <br /><br /><font color=\"#464646\"><font face=\"Arial\"><font face=\"Courier New\"><font style=\"font-size: 15px\"><font size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\">這個發射器有四種速度可選擇。</font><br><br><font color=\"#759FBA\"><br></font><font color=\"#771200\">這就是全圖，那三個開關裝置是重點所在。</font><br><font color=\"#759FBA\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://i1213.photobucket.com/albums/cc476/qaz17899/1652983137.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:400px\"><br></font><font color=\"#771200\">這個為了不重復，多加一條路的是可加快速度裝置。</font><br><font color=\"#759FBA\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://i1213.photobucket.com/albums/cc476/qaz17899/1652983139.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:400px\"><br></font><font color=\"#771200\">這個是pulser，第二段速度控制。</font><br><font color=\"#759FBA\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://i1213.photobucket.com/albums/cc476/qaz17899/1652983140.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:400px\"><br></font><font color=\"#771200\">接下來要講要怎麼控制速度。</font></font></font><font size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\">1是開啟　0是關閉。 </font><br><font color=\"#771200\">(開關裝置，往下開啟，往上關閉。)</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">第一種速度（極快）</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">1 0 1</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">第二種速度（稍快）</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">1 1 0</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">第三種速度（三連射）</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">0 0 0</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">第四種速度（稍慢）</font><br><font color=\"#771200\">0 1 0</font><br><br><font color=\"#771200\">全開就是停止運行。</font><br><br><font color=\"#771200\">存檔下載（簡單版）：</font><a href=\"http://www.megaupload.com/?d=OUUF87C5\">http://www.megaupload.com/?d=OUUF87C5</a><br><font color=\"#771200\">存檔下載（複雜版）：</font><a href=\"http://www.megaupload.com/?d=BV0638ND\">http://www.megaupload.com/?d=BV0638ND</a><br><font color=\"#771200\">存檔放置位置：C:\\Documents and Settings\\xp\\Application Data\\.minecraft\\saves</font><br><br><font color=\"#771200\">解壓縮把New World資料夾放入裡面即可。</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font><div><font face=\"'Courier New'\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\"><br></font></font></font></div><div><font face=\"'Courier New'\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\">影片介紹：</font></font></font></div><div><font><font color=\"#771200\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; \"><a href=\"http://www.megavideo.com/?v=T81565TJ\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); \">http://www.megavideo.com/?v=T81565TJ</a></span></font></font></div><div><font face=\"'Courier New'\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\"><br><br></font></font></font><font face=\"'Courier New'\"><font size=\"2\"><font color=\"#771200\"><br></font></font></font><font color=\"#464646\"><font style=\"font-size: 15px\"><font face=\"Arial\"><font color=\"#771200\"><br></font><br><font size=\"2\"><br></font></font></font></font><br><br><br><br></div>",
